{"tid":2267231,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"陳奕迅帶你入青山","createTime":"2020-11-02T02:38:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T16:20:58.000Z","uid":49781,"like":54,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"ed0d42d5603e52806755f0ef9918ad62d2ac87f3","tid":2267231,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:38:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RS1U6n_BQd4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRS1U6n_BQd4&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxRjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=580bb3fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RS1U6n_BQd4</a><br />\n<br />\n第一集【萬水青山總是情】<br />\n<br />\n陳奕迅X 伍莉瑩醫生(青山醫院)<br />\n<br />\n「細細個，的人就叫我入青山」<br />\n<br />\n陳奕迅Eason興起說到。<br />\n<br />\n伍莉瑩醫生做嚮導，做引路，<br />\n<br />\nEason聽到那些遺落在密閉的隔離室,關於傷害至親，和悔疚的故事。<br />\n<br />\nEason又與來回地獄又折返人間的過來人深度談。 隨著日影轉移,細意感受在病房，在走廊，在飯堂的日常。<br />\n<br />\n你帶著各式的好奇和想像前來青山醫院，你看到了另一遍和煦的風景。<br />\n<br />\n編導：謝家豪"},{"pid":"e00a42bc99b43322260835aefb8d45788b29b349","tid":2267231,"uid":49781,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:38:48.000Z","msg":"相比青山，香港更加似一個精神病院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d1d79e7e649860fed9c3313e37647b46de0986e","tid":2267231,"uid":190789,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:43:24.000Z","msg":"寧願入去住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4f4803a830799ef2ed225871c9874072df06e9c","tid":2267231,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d1d79e7e649860fed9c3313e37647b46de0986e","tid":2267231,"uid":190789,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:43:24.000Z","msg":"寧願入去住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:47:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.g