":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:45:17.000Z","msg":"青山醫院有病人擅自離院　院方已報警<br />\n<br />\n青山醫院一名男病人今早擅自離院。院方表示，一名41歲住院男病人，上午9時許由職員陪同下，到院外牙科診所覆診期間擅自離開，青山醫院即時報警及通知病人家屬，並會配合警方的搜索行動。該名病人身高1.75米、中等身材、黑色短髮，當時身穿藍色外套及綠色長褲。院方呼籲，公眾人士若發現有關病人，請馬上致電3661 5810通知屯門警署報案室或致電青山醫院電話2456 7111。院方已向醫管局呈報事件，會繼續與病人家屬聯絡，提供所需協助。<br />\n<br />\nEason做咩走左去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0eb2f8b066ea34fa0ac68678bed51a0c542c1eb","tid":2267231,"uid":360907,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:45:23.000Z","msg":"『Ba Da Ba Ba Ba Ba, i'm lovin' it』<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nnUjeFf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnnUjeFf.jpg&h=7c8c47ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n『你今日食咗金拱門未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />』"},{"pid":"64efe9ce3dda195097634d9b44d47cef3e82cdb4","tid":2267231,"uid":225210,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:46:19.000Z","msg":"咁Eason究竟係黃定藍???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac518d00c6e8707a080da09c393f8552dd0aacb","tid":2267231,"uid":351819,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"64efe9ce3dda195097634d9b44d47cef3e82cdb4","tid":2267231,"uid":225210,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:46:19.000Z","msg":"咁Eason究竟係黃定藍???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T10:30:35.000Z","msg":"似離地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係藍嘅話一早跟左同期嘅雞蓉 千蟬 古巨基 出post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b05f0d1f4739905d8fbb